Week 8 Questions over Reading

1. What is the significance of 7:4? Did the lion turn into a human?

2. I have in some instances heard Satan referred to as the "Little Horn". Is that reference taken from the account in 7:8?

3. In 7:26 Daniel writes about "the holy people of the Most High" is this in reference to the nation of Israel?

4. In 9:27 is this referring to the anti-christ? "27 He will confirm a covenant with many for one ‘seven.’ In the middle of the ‘seven’ he will put an end to sacrifice and offering. And at the temple he will set up an abomination that causes desolation, until the end that is decreed is poured out on him."

5. The great prince Michael, is this Michael the angel?
